sentences: Andrea Lauren Brown (born 1973) is an American soprano and second prize winner of the 2003 ARD International Music Competition.
Andrea Lauren Brown (born 1973) is an American soprano and second prize winner of the 2003 ARD International Music Competition.
In 2003 she achieved second prize in the singing category at the ARD International Music Competition.
